    set-variable %charset-names  "|ISO-8859|ISO-8859 with box chars|Windows ANSI|Windows OEM|Windows Greek|Windows Turkish|Windows Central Europe|Windows Cyrillic|PC Code Page 437|PC Code Page 850|Cyrillic koi8-r|Plain Text|"
